  <thing id="fStubborWL" name="Stubborn" description="You are exceptionally headstrong and bull-headed. It is difficult to sway you from your intended course of action.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain a +1 bonus on Will saves and a +2 bonus to Intimidate skill checks." compset="Feat" summary="You get a +2 bonus on Intimidate checks and +1 to WIll saves." uniqueness="useronce">
