  <thing id="cMasWorMou" name="Word of Mouth" description="{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Craft (specific skill) 3 ranks.\n\nThe master craftsman&#146;s skill at his craft becomes widely known. Select a Craft skill. With this knack, a week&#146;s worth of dedicated work earns the master craftsman a number of steel pieces equal to his Craft check, rather than half his Craft check.\n\nThis knack may be taken more than once. Each time, it applies to a different Craft skill." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Chosen Craft skill earns 2x normal money per week.">
