  <thing id="cMasCelebr" name="Celebrity" description="The master performer has achieved a certain level of widespread fame. Select a Perform skill. With this knack, the master performer&apos;&#129;s talents are able to command a higher price for performances with that skill. The master performer can earn twice the amount listed for an evening&#129;&apos;s work based on her Perform check result.\n\nThis knack may be taken more than once. Each time, it applies to a different Perform skill." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Chosen Perform skill earns 2x normal money per evening.">
