  <thing id="cMasCoordi" name="Coordinate" description="{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Diplomacy 3 ranks.\n\nThe master performer has a knack for getting people to work together. When the master performer can spend a full round directing his allies and makes a DC 10 Diplomacy check, the performer provides any of his allies within 30 feet a +1 bonus on their attack rolls and skill checks. The bonus lasts for a number of rounds equal to the master performer&#146;s Charisma modifier. The master performer can coordinate a number of allies equal to one-half his master level, rounded down (to a minimum of one ally).\n\nThis knack can be taken more than once. The bonuses on attack rolls and skill checks stack, and the number of rounds the bonuses last increases by +1 for each additional selection." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Full rd, DC10 Diplomacy chk gives allies in 30 ft bonus to att/skill for some rds.">
