  endif]]></validate>
      </prereq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cMasInspGr" name="Greater Inspiration" description="{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Inspiration, Perform 6 ranks.\n\nThe master performer can inspire allies to even greater heights with performances, bolstering them and improving their chances of success. An ally must listen to and observe the master performer for a full round for the greater inspiration to take hold, and the hero must make a DC 15 Perform check. The effect lasts for a number of rounds equal to the character&#146;s Charisma modifier.\n\nAn inspired ally gains an additional +1 morale bonus on saving throws, attack rolls, and damage rolls, which stacks with the bonus from inspiration for a total of a +3 morale bonus.\n\nA master performer cannot inspire himself. The character can inspire a number of allies equal to one-half his master performer level, rounded down (to a minimum of one ally)." compset="CustomSpec" summary="X allies watch 1 rd, +3 morale bon to save, att, &amp; dam for Y rds (DC15 Perform)." uniqueness="unique">
