  <thing id="cMasClient" name="Loyal Clientele" description="The master professional&#146;s skill at his trade becomes widely known. Select a Profession skill. With this knack, the master professional is able to command a higher price for his services with that skill. For a week&#146;s worth of dedicated work the master professional can earn a number of steel pieces equal to his Profession check, rather than half his Profession check.\n\nThis knack may be taken more than once. Each time, it applies to a different Profession skill." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Chosen Profession skill earns 2x normal money per week.">
