  <thing id="sClr2HealH" name="Healing Hand" description="For the duration of the spell, your touch will channel positive energy, allowing you to restore a little bit of health to any living creature you touch. Each round, as a standard action, your touch will heal 1 point of damage. As a full round action, you may heal 1 point of damage to up to six creatures within reach. This spell can be used repeatedly on the same creature, or it can be spread among multiple creatures as need requires. As with cure spells, this spell deals damage to undead instead of curing their wounds. An undead creature can apply spell resistance, and can attempt a Will save to negate the damage.\n\nThis spell is most often used during large-scale battles, where a little bit of healing must go a long way." compset="Spell" summary="Touch heals 1 damage, use full round action to touch up to 6 adjacent allies">
