  <thing id="sMysLifeSi" name="Lifesight" description="Calling upon the vibrant forces of life, you are able to detect the general health and well-being of creatures within the spell&#146;s range. You instantly know whether each creature within the area is dead, injured (more than half total hp remaining), wounded (between 1 hp and half total hp), diseased or poisoned (although you cannot tell what type of disease or poison is infecting the creature), near death (0 hp), dying (-1 through &#150;10 hp), an undead, or neither alive nor dead (such as a construct). {i}Lifesight{/i} sees through any spell or ability that allows creatures to feign life or death." compset="Spell" summary="Know state of creatures in a 30 ft cone">
