  <thing id="cTnkRemDi1" name="Remarkable Discovery" description="You occasionally make incredible leaps of intuitive logic which open up new ideas or ways to accomplish tasks. At 3rd level, and at 6th and 9th level, you gain a bonus feat from the following list, so long as you meet the prerequisites: Armor Proficiency (medium), Armor Proficiency (heavy), Deft Hands, Diligent, Exotic Weapon Proficiency, Improved Shield Bash, Martial Weapon Proficiency, Nimble Fingers, Rapid Reload, Skill Focus, and Weapon Finesse. If you have levels in spellcasting classes, you may choose an item creation feat if you meet the prerequisites." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain a bonus feat from certain list">
