  <thing id="cTnkGranDe" name="Grand Design" description="Upon reaching 10th level, you learn to see the world in its full and glorious intricacy, beyond the mundane and simple outlook of others. You gain a bonus to all saving throws against mind-affecting spells and spell-like effects equal to your Intelligence bonus (if any) and may substitute your Intelligence bonus (if any) for your Wisdom bonus on any Listen, Spot, or Sense Motive check." compset="ClSpecial">
